  ('medical-tech-moex-01968', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-114-9168e375', 'sub-medical-tech-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '從  三群人檢測血中血小板生成素（thrombopoietin, TPO）濃度：正常對照組、再生不良性貧血（aplastic anemia）及原發性血小板過多症（essential thrombocythemia）。結果如圖所示，各組排列最可能是下列何 者？', '["①  正常對照組，②再生不良性貧血，③原發性血小板過多症", "①  正常對照組，②原發性血小板過多症，③再生不良性貧血", "①  原發性血小板過多症，②正常對照組，③再生不良性貧血", "①  原發性血小板過多症，②再生不良性貧血，③正常對照組"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:14:06+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "f5202b821bd2", "answer_pdf_sha1": "f70a89a52d13", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114020", "c": "308", "s": "0501", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床血液學與血庫學", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第一次專技人員高等考試醫師牙醫師中醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師考試", "original_question_number": 51, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-01969', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-114-9168e375', 'sub-medical-tech-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '初  級止血作用如圖所示。（A）血小板在受傷後露出之sub-endothelium滾動，（B）滾動後接著附著，（C） 最後血小板進行凝集作用。在（A）步驟中的血小板受器與其對應sub-endothelium之配體（ligand）各分別 為何？', '["G lycoprotein Ib/IX/V及von Willebrand factor", "G lycoprotein IIb/IIIa及fibrinogen", "G lycoprotein IIb/IIIa及collagen", "G lycoprotein Ib/IX/V及collagen"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:14:06+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "f5202b821bd2", "answer_pdf_sha1": "f70a89a52d13", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114020", "c": "308", "s": "0501", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床血液學與血庫學", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第一次專技人員高等考試醫師牙醫師中醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師考試", "original_question_number": 52, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
